tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE UserInteractions ( user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, interaction_type VARCHAR(50), interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP, interaction_description TEXT )
CREATE TABLE FeedbackHistory ( feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, user_id UUID, feedback_text TEXT, feedback_timestamp TIMESTAMP )

CREATE TABLE user_interaction (
    interaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
    feedback_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP,
    feedback_details TEXT,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE user_history (
    history_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    history_date TIMESTAMP,
    history_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE FeedbackHistory (
    feedback_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_time TIMESTAMP,
    feedback_rating INT,
    feedback_comments TEXT
);
